        "timestamp": "2018-05-17 15:45:21.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nMadeep, Thanks for verify the submission.  Could you please merge the change?   \nOur plan is actually to keep the latest tag on the master branch going forward.  After you cut the release branch we will change the tags on release branch to fixed numbers, but master will remain using \"latest\".  If you see any potential issue with this approach, please kindly let us know.",
